{
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "description": "Template dashboard for Emporia Vue energy monitoring. Auto-discovers devices from InfluxDB.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "code": {"language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false},
        "content": "## Emporia Vue Energy Monitor\n\nThis dashboard auto-discovers your Emporia Vue devices. Use the dropdowns above to select which devices to display.\n\n**Quick Start:** Select your main meter in \"Main Device\" and individual circuits in \"Selected Devices\" to customize the view.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "influxdb"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": {"mode": "normal"},
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "unit": "watt"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3},
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "sortBy": "Mean", "sortDesc": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "all", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "alias": "$tag_device_name",
          "query": "SELECT mean(\"usage\") FROM \"energy_usage\" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), \"device_name\" fill(null)",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "All Devices - Power Consumption",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "influxdb"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 70,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": {"mode": "normal"},
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "unit": "watt"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 11},
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "all", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "alias": "$tag_device_name",
          "query": "SELECT mean(\"usage\") FROM \"energy_usage\" WHERE (\"device_name\" =~ /^$selected_devices$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), \"device_name\" fill(null)",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Selected Devices - Power",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "influxdb"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "stacking": {"mode": "none"},
            "spanNulls": true
          },
          "unit": "watt"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 11},
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "all", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "alias": "Total Power",
          "query": "SELECT mean(\"usage\") FROM \"energy_usage\" WHERE (\"device_name\" = '$main_device') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Main Meter - $main_device",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "influxdb"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 3000},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 5000},
              {"color": "red", "value": 8000}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "watt",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 15000
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 19},
      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "query": "SELECT last(\"usage\") FROM \"energy_usage\" WHERE (\"device_name\" = '$main_device') AND $timeFilter",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Current Power",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "influxdb"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 10},
              {"color": "red", "value": 25}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "kwatth",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 50
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 19},
      "id": 11,
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false},
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "query": "SELECT INTEGRAL(\"usage\") / 3600000 FROM \"energy_usage\" WHERE (\"device_name\" = '$main_device') AND $timeFilter",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Energy Used (kWh)",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "influxdb"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"steps": [{"color": "blue", "value": null}, {"color": "green", "value": 100}]},
          "unit": "watt",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 5000
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 3, "x": 12, "y": 19},
      "id": 20,
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}},
      "targets": [{"query": "SELECT last(\"usage\") FROM \"energy_usage\" WHERE (\"device_name\" =~ /^$selected_devices$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY \"device_name\" LIMIT 1", "rawQuery": true, "refId": "A"}],
      "title": "Device 1",
      "type": "gauge",
      "repeat": "selected_devices",
      "repeatDirection": "h",
      "maxPerRow": 4
    },
    {
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 27},
      "id": 101,
      "options": {
        "code": {"language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false},
        "content": "### Energy Consumption by Device (kWh)\n\nThe table below shows energy consumption for all devices during the selected time period.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "influxdb"},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
