    {
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 41},
      "id": 102,
      "options": {
        "code": {"language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false},
        "content": "---\n\n### Customization Guide\n\n**To add individual device gauges:**\n1. Duplicate an existing gauge panel (click panel title → More → Duplicate)\n2. Edit the panel and modify the query's `device_name` filter\n3. Adjust thresholds and max values for the specific device\n\n**Query for current power (Watts):**\n```sql\nSELECT last(\"usage\") FROM \"energy_usage\" WHERE (\"device_name\" = 'YOUR_DEVICE_NAME') AND $timeFilter\n```\n\n**Query for energy consumption (kWh):**\n```sql\nSELECT INTEGRAL(\"usage\") / 3600000 FROM \"energy_usage\" WHERE (\"device_name\" = 'YOUR_DEVICE_NAME') AND $timeFilter\n```\n\n**Find your device names:** Check the dropdown menus above or run this query in InfluxDB:\n```sql\nSHOW TAG VALUES FROM \"energy_usage\" WITH KEY = \"device_name\"\n```",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Customization Guide",
      "type": "text"
    }
